645
00:34:18,131 --> 00:34:20,332
I was thinking about taking a stroll
since I'm better.

646
00:34:21,571 --> 00:34:22,971
I'll leave you two to talk.

647
00:34:23,292 --> 00:34:25,011
I'll go tidy up and close the shop.

648
00:34:27,852 --> 00:34:28,776
- Danqing.
- Chengfeng.

649
00:34:28,971 --> 00:34:30,172
Thank you for the antidote.

650
00:34:30,812 --> 00:34:32,011
I will always remember it.

651
00:34:32,252 --> 00:34:32,852
Let's go outside.

652
00:34:34,292 --> 00:34:35,411
No, Zishan.

653
00:34:35,411 --> 00:34:36,292
I've got plans today.

654
00:34:36,611 --> 00:34:38,292
(Danqing Winery)
I'll invite you to my place next time.

655
00:34:39,252 --> 00:34:39,931
I'll leave you here.

656
00:34:40,292 --> 00:34:41,411
- I won't see you out.
- Zishan.

657
00:34:45,051 --> 00:34:46,852
We practiced martial arts together.

658
00:34:47,531 --> 00:34:48,692
I always trust and respect you.

659
00:34:51,491 --> 00:34:53,451
You should be very clear
about what's on my mind.

660
00:34:54,212 --> 00:34:56,172
Right, I am very clear

661
00:34:56,971 --> 00:34:57,652
about your thoughts.

662
00:34:58,332 --> 00:34:59,011
But let me tell you.

663
00:35:00,531 --> 00:35:01,091
Impossible.

664
00:35:02,131 --> 00:35:03,971
Zishan, you know me.

665
00:35:04,531 --> 00:35:06,411
- I never go to a brothel.
- That's not the question.

666
00:35:07,491 --> 00:35:09,212
No matter what else you do,

667
00:35:09,571 --> 00:35:10,372
I support you.

668
00:35:10,931 --> 00:35:11,732
But only Danqing.

669
00:35:12,411 --> 00:35:14,131
I don't agree with you
being so close to her.

670
00:35:15,252 --> 00:35:15,852
You don't agree?

671
00:35:16,611 --> 00:35:18,812
Zishan, you are just Danqing's brother.

672
00:35:20,451 --> 00:35:20,931
Yes.

673
00:35:22,332 --> 00:35:23,332
But that can change.

674
00:35:25,292 --> 00:35:26,091
You mean...

675
00:35:33,332 --> 00:35:33,928
Alright.

676
00:35:34,772 --> 00:35:36,212
It's up to Danqing's choice.

677
00:35:37,732 --> 00:35:38,451
Fair competition.

678
00:35:39,332 --> 00:35:39,976
Fair competition.

679
00:35:43,732 --> 00:35:44,808
- Danqing.
- Danqing.

680
00:35:45,332 --> 00:35:47,212
General, why are you still here?

681
00:35:47,212 --> 00:35:48,372
Are you going with us?

682
00:35:48,692 --> 00:35:49,051
Yes.

683
00:35:49,051 --> 00:35:49,772
He said he'd return.

684
00:35:51,172 --> 00:35:53,252
Danqing, I've never been
to the temple fair either.

685
00:35:53,852 --> 00:35:54,451
Let me join you.

686
00:35:54,451 --> 00:35:55,051
Another time then.

687
00:35:55,611 --> 00:35:56,692
Let's do it another day.

688
00:35:57,011 --> 00:35:59,332
It's rare that we siblings
can go out and relax.

689
00:35:59,332 --> 00:36:00,172
You can understand.

690
00:36:01,332 --> 00:36:02,408
