700
00:36:59,131 --> 00:37:01,732
Why not take one each?

701
00:37:01,732 --> 00:37:02,971
Good things come in pairs.

702
00:37:04,252 --> 00:37:05,131
Look at those people.

703
00:37:05,571 --> 00:37:06,571
Aren't they also looking

704
00:37:06,852 --> 00:37:09,091
for the one with the same flowers?

705
00:37:11,571 --> 00:37:13,292
Danqing, pick a bouquet.

706
00:37:14,091 --> 00:37:14,971
Which one would you like?

707
00:37:16,172 --> 00:37:17,011
I'll pick

708
00:37:17,411 --> 00:37:18,491
