709
00:37:18,652 --> 00:37:20,011
Such a considerate gentleman.

710
00:37:20,252 --> 00:37:22,248
Miss, you are truly fortunate.

711
00:37:22,652 --> 00:37:24,692
Madam, you are joking. He is my brother.

712
00:37:30,952 --> 00:37:31,531
Thank you.

713
00:37:34,812 --> 00:37:36,520
Zishan, I want to eat Tanghulu.

714
00:37:37,091 --> 00:37:39,051
Okay, wait here for me.
I'll go and buy it.

715
00:37:39,051 --> 00:37:39,411
Okay.

716
00:37:40,491 --> 00:37:41,411
