727
00:39:12,531 --> 00:39:14,051
Why is it you?

728
00:39:17,212 --> 00:39:18,332
Liar!

729
00:39:18,652 --> 00:39:20,051
Catch him! Don't let him get away!

730
00:39:20,372 --> 00:39:21,512
I am the Flower God of this year.

731
00:39:22,091 --> 00:39:22,632
Let's go.

732
00:39:24,051 --> 00:39:24,812
Thanks a lot, dude.

